In re the MATTER OF Q.A.R.; Jeffrey Thomas Parks, Appellant,
v.
McKay J. LANNIGAN, Respondent. WD 82040 Missouri Court of Appeals, Western District. ORDER FILED: May 14, 2019 Frank Flaspohler, Fayette, MO, Counsel for Appellant, Parks. Deborah Riekhof, Fayette, MO, Counsel for Respondent, Lannigan Andrew Jones, Kansas City, MO, Counsel for Respondent, Dept. Social Serv. Before Division Three: Thomas H. Newton, Presiding Judge, Anthony Rex Gabbert, and Edward R. Ardini, Judges

ORDER

Per Curiam:

Mr. Jeffrey Parks appeals from a judgment of the Boone County Circuit Court modifying the terms of the care, custody, and support of his minor child, Q.R. For reasons stated in the memorandum provided to the parties, the judgment of the trial court is affirmed in accordance with Rule 84.16(b).
